    </vim-test-answers>
  </vim-test-question>
</vim-test>

<p>The boat started floating out towards the sea and also, at the same time, the weather changed. It became very windy and the sea got choppy and we were quite scared. 
So, when we looked in the boat, the radio didn't work, so we couldn't ask for any help. We thought we were gonna be stuck here all night because we had no way of contacting anybody.
But in the end, it was OK because my girlfriend managed  to find the telephone number of the people who gave us the boat, so, after about half an hour maybe, 
they came and rescued us, but at the time it was, er, we were very worried and very scared.</p>

